wning and Suffocating}</p>\n<p>You can hold your breath for a number of rounds equal to 5 + your Constitution modifier. Reduce your remaining air by 1 round at the end of each of your turns, or by 2 if you attacked or cast any spells that turn.</p>\n<p>You also lose 1 round worth of air each time you are critically hit or critically fail a save against a damaging effect. If you speak (including Casting a Spell) you lose all remaining air.</p>"},"duration":{"expiry":null,"sustained":false,"unit":"unlimited","value":-1},"level":{"value":1},"publication":{"license":"ORC","remaster":true,"title":"Starfinder Player Core"},"rules":[{"key":"ActiveEffectLike","mode":"add","path":"flags.system.remainingAir.rounds","value":"5 + @actor.abilities.con.mod"},{"itemId":"{item|id}","key":"ItemAlteration","mode":"override","property":"badge-max","value":"@actor.flags.system.remainingAir.rounds"},{"key":"Note","selector":"attack","text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.AttackOrSpells","title":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label"},{"itemType":"spell","key":"ItemAlteration","label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label","mode":"add","priority":121,"property":"description","value":[{"text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.AttackOrSpells"},{"predicate":[{"not":"item:trait:subtle"}],"text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Speak"}]},{"itemType":"action","key":"ItemAlteration","label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label","mode":"add","predicate":["item:trait:auditory"],"priority":121,"property":"description","value":[{"text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Speak"}]},{"itemType":"feat","key":"ItemAlteration","label":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label","mode":"add","predicate":["item:trait:auditory"],"priority":121,"property":"description","value":[{"text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Speak"}]},{"key":"Note","outcome":["criticalFailure"],"predicate":["damaging-effect"],"selector":"saving-throw","text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.LoseOneRound","title":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label"},{"key":"Note","outcome":["criticalSuccess"],"selector":"damage-received","text":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.LoseOneRound","title":"PF2E.SpecificRule.RemainingAir.Label"}],"start":{"initiative":null,"value":0},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"traits":{"value":[]},"slug":"effect-remaining-air","_migration":{"version":0.955,"previous":null}},"type":"effect","_stats":{"coreVersion":"13.348","systemId":"sf2e","systemVersion":"0.0.8","compendiumSource":"Compendium.sf2e.other-effects.Item.2u26bmArDPuoCljc"},"effects":[]},{"_id":"9c93NfZpENofiGUp","img":"icons/environment/creatures/horse-tan.webp","name":"Effect: Mounted","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>See @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.journals.JournalEntry.S55aqwWIzpQRFhcq.JournalEntryPage.OiRwxbfLNUniLg15#mounted-combat]{Mounted Combat}</p>\n<p>You take a –2 circumstance penalty to Reflex saves while mounted.</p>"},"duration":{"expiry":null,"sustained":false,"unit":"unlimited","value":-1},"level":{"value":1},"publication":{"license":"ORC","remaster":true,"title":"Starfinder Player Core"},"rules":[{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"reflex","type":"circumstance","value":-2}],"start":{"initiative":null,"value":0},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"traits":{"rarity":"common","value":[]},"slug":"effect-mounted","_migration":{"version":0.955,"previous":null}},"type":"effect","_stats":{"coreVersion":"13.348","systemId":"sf2e","systemVersion":"0.0.8","compendiumSource":"Compendium.sf2e.other-effects.Item.9c93NfZpENofiGUp"},"effects":[]},{"_id":"AHMUpMbaVkZ5A1KX","img":"systems/sf2e/icons/spells/efficient-apport.webp","name":"Effect: Aid","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.HCl3pzVefiv9ZKQW]{Aid}</p>\n<p>You gain a circumstance bonus to the aided check based on the result of your ally's Aid check.</p>"},"duration":{"expiry":"turn-start","sustained":false,"unit":"rounds","value":1},"level":{"value":1},"publication":{"license":"ORC","remaster":true,"title":"Starfinder Player Core"},"rules":