[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.Dt6B1slsBy8ipJu9]{Disarm}</p>\n<p>You take a –2 circumstance penalty to attacks using the targeted item. Further attempts to Disarm you gain a +2 circumstance bonus.</p>"},"duration":{"expiry":null,"sustained":false,"unit":"unlimited","value":-1},"level":{"value":1},"publication":{"license":"ORC","remaster":true,"title":"Starfinder Player Core"},"rules":[{"choices":{"attacks":true,"predicate":["item:equipped",{"not":"item:category:unarmed"}]},"flag":"disarmWeakenedGrasp","key":"ChoiceSet","prompt":"PF2E.SpecificRule.Prompt.Weapon"},{"key":"FlatModifier","selector":"{item|flags.system.rulesSelections.disarmWeakenedGrasp}-attack","type":"circumstance","value":-2},{"affects":"origin","key":"EphemeralEffect","selectors":"skill-check","uuid":"Compendium.sf2e.other-effects.Item.EpvyTaklBQAOr1eT"}],"start":{"initiative":null,"value":0},"tokenIcon":{"show":true},"traits":{"rarity":"common","value":[]},"slug":"effect-disarm-success","_migration":{"version":0.955,"previous":null}},"type":"effect","_stats":{"coreVersion":"13.348","systemId":"sf2e","systemVersion":"0.0.8","compendiumSource":"Compendium.sf2e.other-effects.Item.PuDS0DEq0CnaSIFV"},"effects":[]},{"_id":"TGGdM7XnjQkkijK7","img":"systems/sf2e/icons/effects/treat-disease.webp","name":"Effect: Treat Disease","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.actions.Item.TC7OcDa7JlWbqMaN]{Treat Disease}</p>\n<p>You gain a circumstance bonus or penalty to your next save against the disease.</p>"},"duration":{"expiry":null,"sustained":false,"unit":"unlimited","value":-1},"level":{"value":1},"publication":{"license":"ORC","remaster":true,"title":"Starfinder Player Core"},"rules":[{"choices":[{"label":"PF2E.Check.Result.Degree.Check.criticalSuccess","predicate":[{"or":["parent:context:check:outcome:3",{"not":{"gte":["parent:context:check:outcome",0]}}]}],"value":4},{"label":"PF2E.Check.Result.Degree.Check.success","predicate":[{"or":["parent:context:check:outcome:2",{"not":{